privacy@vividpicks.com
.
• Social Media Platforms and Networks
. We encourage you to review your privacy options and settings with the social media platforms and networks you use to understand what choices you have about sharing information from those platforms and networks with us.
• Email Choices
. You can opt out of marketing or advertising emails by contacting us at
privacy@vividpicks.com
or by utilizing the "unsubscribe" link or following other instructions noted in marketing or advertising emails you receive from us. Please note that opting out of receiving marketing or advertising emails from us will not apply to transactional communications or legal notices, for example, emails about your contest transactions, ticket orders, or about changes to our terms, policies, or business practices.
• Managing Cookies
. We, our affiliates and third parties may use cookies such as Google Analytics in order to understand how you interact with our Site and Apps. If you wish to prevent your data from being used by Google Analytics, Google has developed the Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on available https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout/. Additionally, we, our affiliates and third parties may use other tracking technologies such as pixel tags, web beacons, SDKs, scripts and/or similar technologies on our Site, Apps and emails. Some of these cookies and similar technologies are necessary for the Site to function, while some optional technologies are used for certain functional purposes and to measure and analyze the performance of our ads on third party platforms.  You can activate settings on your Internet browser to refuse the setting of some or all cookies, or take steps to remove existing cookies from your browser if you wish. Please keep in mind, however, that if you use your Internet browser settings to block all cookies (including essential/required cookies) you may not be able to access all or parts of our Site and Apps and services. For further information about managing cookies, please visit
www.allaboutcookies.org
. Please note that disabling or clearing cookies also may affect cookie-based opt-outs by either preventing you from using such cookie-based opt-outs or clearing opt-outs that you have previously set, in which case you would have to revisit the applicable pages/tools and renew your opt-out after clearing cookies. In addition, our Site is not designed to respond to “Do Not Track” signals.
• Mobile Devices
. Your mobile device may offer settings relating to cookies, pixel tags, SDKs, scripts and other similar technologies. We encourage to you to visit your device's help menu to learn about your options to limit tracking when using your device.
• Interest-Based Advertising Choices
. As described above, we may use  audience builders and similar tools offered by third parties, and engage in interest-based advertising on third party sites. To understand your choices for receiving more relevant advertising provided on across other websites and online services, please review the information below:
